# Changelog

All notable changes to **Echos of Nou** will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

> **Versioning quick reference**
> `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` →
> - **MAJOR** — breaking save-file or platform changes
> - **MINOR** — new biomes, masks, modes, or significant content
> - **PATCH** — bug fixes, balance tweaks, performance improvements

---

