## [1.0.0] — 2026-05-06

Initial public release. The "suffering platformer" prototype is feature-complete for the prototype scope.

### Added
- Vertical platforming core loop: charged jump, auto-walk, fall recovery
- Four Nuo Masks with unique traversal abilities:
  - The Pathfinder (aerial dash)
  - The Mountain Breaker (wall cling / reverse bounce)
  - The Eightfold King (gravity inversion)
  - The Nuo-Fire Warlord (double jump)
- Three game modes: Normal, Story, and Speedrun
- Checkpoint system with shrine activation and fall protection
- Four vertical biomes:
  - Misty River Pass
  - Valley of Suspended Coffins
  - Stilted Cliff Village
  - Ancestral Shrine Peak
- Cyber-folk soundtrack with Suona accents on critical jumps
- Builds for Windows, macOS, and Android

### Known Issues
- iOS build not yet available
- Some checkpoint transitions may have a one-frame visual hitch
- Audio mixing balance may need adjustment in headphones vs. speakers
